IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TC401P.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 PRINCIPAL    PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3 VALUE 100000.00.
01 RATE         PIC S9(3)V9(4) COMP-3 VALUE 5.2500.
01 INTEREST     PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3.
01 TOTAL        PIC S9(8)V99 COMP-3.
01 DISPLAY-AMT  PIC $$,$$$,$$9.99-.
*> COMP-3 arithmetic must use fixed-point decimal math, never binary float.
*> The edited picture output for this fixture is exactly two spaces after "=":
*> TOTAL=  $105,250.00 
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    COMPUTE INTEREST = PRINCIPAL * RATE / 100.
    COMPUTE TOTAL = PRINCIPAL + INTEREST.
    MOVE TOTAL TO DISPLAY-AMT.
    DISPLAY "TOTAL=" DISPLAY-AMT.
    STOP RUN.
